{"id":"api/core/Input","title":"Input","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/Input\", \"name\": \"Input\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L961-L962\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L961-L962\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"input\">Input<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Input#input\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    \n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  \n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>选项</th><th>说明</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Input#bindingPropertyName\">\n          <code>bindingPropertyName</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td><p translation-result=\"on\">一个装饰器，用来把某个类字段标记为输入属性，并且提供配置元数据。\n声明一个可供数据绑定的输入属性，在变更检测期间，Angular 会自动更新它。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Decorator that marks a class field as an input property and supplies configuration metadata.\nDeclares a data-bound input property, which Angular automatically updates\nduring change detection.</p>\n\n</td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">选项<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Input#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"bindingPropertyName\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead><tr><th>\n      <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n        <h3 id=\"bindingpropertyname\">bindingPropertyName<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Input#bindingpropertyname\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L866-L919\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L866-L919\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">一个装饰器，用来把某个类字段标记为输入属性，并且提供配置元数据。\n声明一个可供数据绑定的输入属性，在变更检测期间，Angular 会自动更新它。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Decorator that marks a class field as an input property and supplies configuration metadata.\nDeclares a data-bound input property, which Angular automatically updates\nduring change detection.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n          bindingPropertyName: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">你可以提供一个可选的仅供模板中使用的名字，在组件实例化时，会把这个名字映射到可绑定属性上。\n默认情况下，输入绑定的名字就是这个可绑定属性的原始名称。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You can supply an optional name to use in templates when the\ncomponent is instantiated, that maps to the\nname of the bound property. By default, the original\nname of the bound property is used for input binding.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">下面的例子创建了一个带有两个输入属性的组件，其中一个还指定了绑定名。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example creates a component with two input properties,\none of which is given a special binding name.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'bank-account',\n  <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `\n    Bank Name: {{bankName}}\n    Account Id: {{id}}\n  `\n})\nclass BankAccount {\n  // This property is bound using its original name.\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() bankName: string;\n  // this property value is bound to <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> different property name\n  // when this component is instantiated in <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> template.\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>('account-id') id: string;\n\n  // this property is not bound, and is not automatically updated by Angular\n  normalizedBankName: string;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `\n    &#x3C;bank-account bankName=\"RBC\" account-id=\"4747\">&#x3C;/bank-account>\n  `\n})\n\nclass App {}\n</code-example>\n\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgClass\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/common/NgPlural\n - api/common/NgStyle\n - api/common/NgSwitch\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/ContentChild\n - api/core/ContentChildren\n - api/core/OnChanges\n - api/core/ViewChild\n - api/core/ViewChildren\n - api/forms/EmailValidator\n - api/forms/FormArrayName\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/FormGroupName\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\n - api/forms/MinLengthValidator\n - api/forms/NgForm\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/NgSelectOption\n - api/forms/PatternValidator\n - api/forms/RadioControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator\n - api/forms/SelectControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\n - api/router/RouterLink\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - api/upgrade/UpgradeAdapter\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - api/upgrade/static/downgradeComponent\n - guide/aot-compiler\n - guide/attribute-directives\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/custom-elements\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n - guide/dynamic-component-loader\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/elements\n - guide/form-validation\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/hierarchical-dependency-injection\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/ngmodule-faq\n - guide/structural-directives\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n - guide/upgrade-performance\n - tutorial/toh-pt3\n - tutorial/toh-pt6\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/core/Input#bindingPropertyName\n - api/core/Input#bindingpropertyname\n - api/core/Input#input\n - api/core/Input#options\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L866-L919\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L961-L962\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L866-L919\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/7.2.0-rc.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L961-L962\n-->"}